---
title: No Chop Pesto Chicken & Potato Skillet No Knife Work & Only One Pot!
description: Our easiest-ever meals with no knifework and only one pot, done in a flash! Layer seasoned pre-cooked potato slices, flavorful dark meat chicken, and fresh green beans all in one pan. While the potatoes and chicken cook, the green beans steam to perfection on top. You’ll drizzle it all with our savory, herbaceous basil pesto, and serve it up in no time at all.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67f3ba3a27b8e5819ffeba57-f1054888.jpeg
